OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMinister asks council to   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fend four-day week trial    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The local government minister has      
OL,6, formally requested a council ends its  
OL,7, trial of a four-day week "immediately" 
OL,8, over concerns about "value for money". 
OL,10,FSouth Cambridgeshire District Council's
OL,11,Ftrial was due to run until 2024, but in
OL,12,Fa letter, Lee Rowley said such an      
OL,13,Fapproach could breach its legal duties.
OL,15,FThe Liberal Democrat-led council is the
OL,16,Ffirst in the UK to trial the system.   
OL,18,FDefending the scheme, leader Bridget   
OL,19,FSmith said it had helped address a     
OL,20,Freliance on expensive agency staff.    
